== Overview ==
The Phoenix Laser is the most powerful single chambered [[:Category:Weapons (Lasers)|laser]] available to cybots. It out performs the [[Baron Battery]] when dealing with deflections.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Phoenix Laser can be bought in the workshop after obtaining [[Magma Technology]].
